						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">"Reading 1 PPU clock before VBL should suppress setting."</div>
<br />
<br />- <strong>Read</strong> means <span style="text-decoration: underline">LDA $2002</span>, and 1 PPU clock before would occur right before effectively reading 2002.
<br />
<br />- It's not over complicated. ^_^;;</div>

