						<div class="postbody"><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">LDA $2002<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; #&nbsp; address R/W description<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;--- ------- --- ------------------------------------------<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1&nbsp; &nbsp; PC&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;R&nbsp; fetch opcode, increment PC<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2&nbsp; &nbsp; PC&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;R&nbsp; fetch low byte of address, increment PC<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3&nbsp; &nbsp; PC&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;R&nbsp; fetch high byte of address, increment PC<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4&nbsp; address&nbsp; R&nbsp; read from effective address<br /></div>
